reviewText: This is a really good cd. It has a hip hop feel to it. Really good for kids 3 and under. Well pleased

I didn't know what to expect, but surely something a lot more professional. The songs were the same as both cd volumes, nothing original. The kids that are "acting" look lost and confused, especially while trying to sing along with the music. If it didn't keep my interest it's definitely not going to keep my child's.

I bought the dvd for my 16 month old nephews and 13 month old cousin.  All loved to listen to the songs na dsounds made during the dvd.  Mostly listen to the songs from the dvd instead of watching it.
